Package org.eclipse.cdt.core

Interface IErrorParserNamed

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, IErrorParser
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ErrorParserNamedWrapper, FixitErrorParser, RegexErrorParser
    public interface IErrorParserNamed
extends IErrorParser, Cloneable
    Extension of IErrorParser interface to attach id and names to an error parser. Clients must implement Object.clone() and Object.equals(java.lang.Object) methods to avoid slicing.
    Since:
    5.2
